(8, '21', '21', 'Jordan 1 Low Bred Toe', '21999', '21', 'jordan-1-low-bred-toe', 'jordan-1-low', NULL, 'With its iconic black and red colour blocking, the Jordan 1 Low Bred Toe is inspired by the 2018 Air Jordan 1 High Bred Toe. For the new Jordan 1 Low Bred Toe, Jordan Brand has resurrected the spirit of 2018\'s popular Air Jordan 1 \"Bred Toe.\" While this low-cut version of the modern-day Air Jordan 1 classic closely resembles its predecessor in terms of colour scheme, it also has a few unique material selections and branding embellishments that set it distinct from other jordans. \r\n\r\nWhite, black, and red leather make up the upper, with black and red leather smothering the vamp, Swoosh, alongside the heel and white leather dominating its quarter panel. The design is finished off with an embroidered Wing logo on the heel and a Jumpman tongue label.\r\n\r\nThe Air Jordan 1 Low was originally released in several colourways, mirroring the High releases and served as a casual take on the signature high-top. Apart from basketball players, there was another group who immediately took to the AJ1 Low â€“ skateboarders. The skateboarders found that the low-top was more comfortable for tricks. \r\n\r\nGet legit Air Jordan High, Air Jordan Mid, Air Jordan Low and more limited edition sneakers only on House of Sneakers.\r\n\r\nColor Shown: Gym Red/white-black', 'Gym Red/white-black', NULL, '2023-06-26 11:48', 1),
(9, '23', '23', 'Yeezy 350 Onyx', '34999', '34999', '', 'yeezy-350', NULL, 'The Adidas Yeezy 350 V2 Onyx goes back to the fundamentals with a triple-black Primeknit upper, utilizing its muted colour scheme to highlight the intricate details of its design. A modest texture contrast is provided by a sheer mesh side stripe and a canvas heel loop. The Adidas Yeezy 350 V2 Onyx\'s base is cushioned and supported by a matching trademark Boost sole.\r\n\r\nThe flagship shoe model of the Yeezy line is the Yeezy Boost 350, now available as Yeezy Boost 350 v2. Launched in 2015, and 45 iterations later, this is the most popular silhouette in the sneaker collection. Construction-wise, Yeezy Boost 350 features an elastic upper comprised of Adidasâ€™ Primeknit material with Boost midsole cushioning.\r\n\r\nGet the latest Yeezy shoes, Yeezy slides and more limited edition sneakers only on House of Sneakers.\r\n\r\nColor Shown: ONYX/ONYX/ONYX\r\n\r\nNote-Its recommended to order full size up from your standard size', 'Onyx', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:05', 1),
(10, '22', '22', 'Air Jordan 1 High OG Stage Haze Bleached Coral', '29999', '20', '', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'The Air Jordan 1 High OG Stage Haze keeps with the traditional Black Toe aesthetic and has a smooth white leather upper with black overlays and light grey Durabuck heel covers. Jordan Wings Logos on the collars and traditional Nike woven tongue labels give the Air Jordan 1 High OG Stage Haze a vintage vibe. The design is then finished with an Air sole in white and light grey.\r\n\r\nAir Jordan 1 High is the most popular sneaker model ever. The MJ signature sneaker to date excites sneakerheads just as much as it did in the 80s and 90s. The Air Jordan 1 High is on the feet of your favourite celebrity and everywhere on Instagram yet people can never get enough of these sneakers. The canvas for many exciting collaborations and made with premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 High is often the ultimate prize for any sneakerhead.\r\n\r\nGet legit Air Jordan High, Air Jordan Mid, Air Jordan Low and more limited edition sneakers', 'White / Black / Grey Fog / Bleached Coral ', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:06', 1),
(11, '24', '24', 'Yeezy 350 Beluga Reflective', '39999', '39999', '', 'yeezy-350', NULL, 'The Adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Beluga Reflective gives one of Yeezy\'s most well-known designs a reflective makeover.\r\n\r\nThe Adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Beluga Reflective expands on the original Beluga colorway by giving its Primeknit upper reflective properties and speckled orange accents. The design is completed with distinguishing elements including a Boost sole and an orange side stripe. \r\n\r\nThe flagship shoe model of the Yeezy line is the Yeezy Boost 350, now available as Yeezy Boost 350 v2. Launched in 2015, and 45 iterations later, this is the most popular silhouette in the sneaker collection. Construction-wise, Yeezy Boost 350 features an elastic upper comprised of Adidasâ€™ Primeknit material with Boost midsole cushioning.\r\n\r\nGet the latest Yeezy shoes, Yeezy slides and more limited edition sneakers only on House of Sneakers.\r\n\r\nColor Shown: BELUGA/BELUGA/BELUGA\r\n\r\nNote-Its recommended to order full size up from your standard size', 'Beluga', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:11', 1),
(12, '25', '25', 'Air Jordan 1 High OG Bordeaux ', '26999', '26999', 'J1HIGH-BORDEAUX', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'The Air Jordan 1 that started it all for MJ. Jordan 1 Retro High OG Bordeaux makeup gets a large gulp of a brand-new colorway thanks to some heritage colour blocking. The vibrant Bordeaux overlays, laces, and embellishments pop against a crisp White midsole and leather underlays. Metallic Silver Swooshes and Air Jordan Wings branding provide a trophy-like touch to a style that will look even better once you take it out of the box and give it a chance to breathe.\r\n\r\n Jordan 1 Retro High OG Bordeaux features a metallic silver Swoosh and a jewelled Wings logo on the lateral ankle, similar to the CO.JP \'Midnight Navy\' colorway. An OG touch is provided with a woven Nike Air tongue tag atop the gently padded nylon tongue. Under the heel, a conventional two-tone Air Jordan 1 cupsole houses encapsulated Nike Air cushioning.\r\n\r\n Air Jordan 1 High is the most popular sneaker model ever. The MJ signature sneaker to date excites sneakerheads just as much as it did in the 80s and 90s. The Air Jordan 1 High is on the feet of your favourite celebrity and everywhere on Instagram yet people can never get enough of these sneakers. Why is that? Because the colourways are just too good! The canvas for many exciting collaborations and made with premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 High is often the ultimate prize for any sneakerhead\r\n\r\nGet legit Air Jordan High, Air Jordan Mid, Air Jordan Low and more limited edition sneakers only at House of Sneakers.', 'Bordeaux/White/Metalic silver ', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:13', 1),
(13, '26', '26', 'Air Jordan 1 High OG Patent Bred ', '29999', '29999', '', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'Jordan 1 Retro High OG Patent Bred is a glossy update of the famous colorway dressed in the classic hues. Apart from the patent leather structure, the Air Jordan 1â€™s design DNA is unaltered. The upper is primarily black with Varsity Red accents on the toe box, Swoosh, heel overlay, and collar flap. The black nylon tongue has a woven Nike tag, and the lateral collar has a Wings emblem embossed on it. The high-top is built with a durable rubber cupsole and an Air-sole unit encased in lightweight polyurethane.\r\n\r\nThe black and red patent leather top of the Jordan 1 Retro High OG Patent Bred boasts distinctive braided Nike Air tongue labels. The nostalgic look on the Air Jordan 1 is completed with a traditional Wings emblem on the collar and a white with red Air sole.\r\n\r\nAir Jordan 1 High is the most popular sneaker model ever. The MJ signature sneaker to date excites sneakerheads just as much as it did in the 80s and 90s. The Air Jordan 1 High is on the feet of your favourite celebrity and everywhere on Instagram yet people can never get enough of these sneakers. Why is that? Because the colourways are just too good! The canvas for many exciting collaborations and made with premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 High is often the ultimate prize for any sneakerhead. \r\n\r\nGet legit Air Jordan High, Air Jordan Mid, Air Jordan Low and more limited edition sneakers only on House of Sneakers.', 'Black/white/Varsity Red', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:22', 1),
(14, '27', '27', 'Air jordan 1 Retro High OG Light Fusion Red', '22900', '22900', '', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'The Air Jordan 1 Light Fusion Red features a white leather upper with Light Fusion Red overlays and Laser Orange on the Swoosh and ankle wrap. A woven Nike label stitched atop the tongue completes the design.', 'Fusion Red / laser Orange / White / Black', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:26', 1),
(15, '28', '28', 'Jordan 1 High Retro Tokyo Bio Hack', '20999', '20999', '', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'The Air Jordan Retro highlights a unique color way with a white base with contrasting features on the heels and collars. The toe-box falls out with a monochromatic tone on leather.', 'BAROQUE BROWN/BLACK-LASER ORANGE-RACER PINK', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:29', 1),
(16, '29', '29', 'JORDAN 1 RETRO HIGH CO JAPAN NEUTRAL GREY (2020)', '30000', '30000', '', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'The Air Jordan Retro highlights a unique colour way with a white base with contrasting features on the heels and collars. The toe-box falls out with a monochromatic tone on leather', 'Silver/White ', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:32', 1),
(17, '30', '30', 'JORDAN 1 RETRO HIGH OG LOST AND FOUND', '36999', '36999', '', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'The original, most recognizable design is brought back with the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG \"Lost & Found.\" The leather upper, which retains the original release\'s high-cut design from 1985, blends a white base with a black trademark Swoosh and red overlays at the forefoot and heel. On the padded collar, cracked black leather is visible, and the white rubber midsole has a pre-yelled vintage look.\r\n\r\nThe Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG \"Lost & Found\" has a unique packaging which maintains the retro \'80s theme, with a damaged box covered in sale stickers and topped with an off-color replacement lid as a standout feature. An accompanying sales receipt recalls a time when the Air Jordan 1 languished on the racks of mom-and-pop shops before being acquired by lucky buyers.\r\n\r\nAir Jordan 1 High is the most popular sneaker model ever. The MJ signature sneaker to date excites sneakerheads just as much as it did in the 80s and 90s. The Air Jordan 1 High is on the feet of your favourite celebrity and everywhere on Instagram yet people can never get enough of these sneakers. The canvas for many exciting collaborations and made with premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 High is often the ultimate prize for any sneakerhead.\r\n\r\nGet legit Air Jordan High, Air Jordan Mid, Air Jordan Low and more limited edition sneakers only on House of Sneakers.', 'Varsity Red/ Black Sail Muslin', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:36', 1),
(18, '31', '31', 'JORDAN 1 RETRO HIGH OG VISIONAIRE', '23500', '23500', '', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'The distinctive yellow/green color is added to an unusual design in the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Visionaire. Although Nike has eased up throughout the years in terms of colorways, Air Jordan 1s have always depended on main, team-based hues. The Varsity Red tones have been replaced with vivid, neon yellow overlays in this version of the Jordan 1, which adheres to the classic Chicago-style colour blocking.\r\n\r\nThe white leather foundation layers are contrasted with black detailing around the Swooshes, laces, as well as collars, but the remainder of the uppers are identical to the original \"Chicago\" Jordan 1. You also see the standard Jordan \"Wingsâ€ logo on the ankle collars, which complement the uppers and outsoles of the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Visionaire. This particular release also includes a limited-edition shoebox featuring OG-style white and volt packaging. The worn-in look is emphasized by the cracked leather on the collar and the fading laces, which might be a hint at the upcoming Reimagined Air Jordan 1s.\r\n\r\nâ€‹â€‹Air Jordan 1 High is the most popular sneaker model ever. The MJ signature sneaker to date excites sneakerheads just as much as it did in the 80s and 90s. The Air Jordan 1 High is on the feet of your favourite celebrity and everywhere on Instagram yet people can never get enough of these sneakers. The canvas for many exciting collaborations and made with premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 High is often the ultimate prize for any sneakerhead.\r\n\r\nGet legit Air Jordan High, Air Jordan Mid, Air Jordan Low and more limited edition sneakers only on House of Sneakers ', 'Volt / Black / Sail', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:39', 1),
(19, '32', '32', 'JORDAN 1 RETRO HIGH LIGHT SMOKE GREY', '36900', '36900', '', 'jordan-1-high', NULL, 'By combining classic colours from the Air Jordan 1 series in a blocking pattern that re-imagines a colorway mash-up, this rendition of the Jordan 1 Retro High Light Smoke Grey both honours its own heritage and breaks new territory. The Jordan 1 Retro High Light Smoke Grey uses colour blocking and diverse materials to present recognisable colours in a novel manner, akin to the Air Jordan 1 Union LA from 2018. \r\n\r\n The white toe box on this  Air Jordan 1 is offset by grey and red plush suede overlays, all of which come together around a black Swoosh for a modern classic look. The style is completed with black suede heel panelling and Swoosh, a white midsole, and a black outsole. A white leather top with grey suede overlays and a red leather ankle panel makes up the Jordan 1 Retro High Light Smoke Grey.\r\n\r\n Air Jordan 1 High is the most popular sneaker model ever. The MJ signature sneaker to date excites sneakerheads just as much as it did in the 80s and 90s. The Air Jordan 1 High is on the feet of your favourite celebrity and everywhere on Instagram yet people can never get enough of these sneakers. Why is that? Because the colourways are just too good! The canvas for many exciting collaborations and made with premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 High is often the ultimate prize for any sneakerhead. \r\n\r\nGet legit Air Jordan High, Air Jordan Mid, Air Jordan Low and more limited edition sneakers only on House of Sneakers ', 'Light Smoke / Grey / Red', NULL, '2023-06-26 18:43', 1),
